---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = "Zero-Downtime Legacy System Migration Approach | Enterprise Cloud Migration | Jitan Gupta";
const description = "Discover my proven end-to-end approach for migrating legacy systems to cloud-native architectures without disruption. Reduce technical debt while maintaining business continuity.";
const pageTheme = "bg-primary-light";
---
<Layout	title={title} description={description}>
	<section class="bg-gray-100 mx-2">
		<div class="bg-white max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-5 py-5 md:px-15 md:py-10 rounded-b-2xl">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mt-5 md:mt-8 mb-2 font-bold" style="line-height: 1.2;">Migration Approach:<br>
                <span class="text-2xl md:text-4xl">A Proven Framework for Seamless Transitions</span></h1>
            <h3 class="text-gray-900 text-2xl mt-5 mb-2">Why Migrate?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Legacy systems come with technical debt, security vulnerabilities, and scalability limitations. A well-planned migration not only modernizes your tech stack but also improves performance, security, and business agility.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Whether you’re migrating from on-prem to cloud, .NET Framework to .NET Core, or decentralizing authentication, my approach ensures minimal downtime, maximum efficiency, and long-term success.</p>
        
            <!-- Diagram -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 800 600">
                <!-- Background -->
                <rect width="800" height="600" fill="#f8f9fa" rx="10" ry="10"/>
                
                <!-- Title -->
                <text x="400" y="50" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Migration Approach</text>
                
                <!-- Circle Background -->
                <circle cx="400" cy="300" r="220" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#dddddd" stroke-width="2"/>
                
                <!-- Phase Circles -->
                <!-- Assessment -->
                <circle cx="400" cy="120" r="70" fill="#4285f4" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="400" cy="120" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="400" y="110" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Assessment</text>
                <text x="400" y="130" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Understanding current</text>
                <text x="400" y="145" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">system & pain points</text>
                
                <!-- Planning -->
                <circle cx="580" cy="200" r="70" fill="#34a853" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="580" cy="200" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="580" y="190" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Planning</text>
                <text x="580" y="210" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Creating migration</text>
                <text x="580" y="225" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">strategy with rollback</text>
                
                <!-- Decision Making -->
                <circle cx="580" cy="400" r="70" fill="#fbbc05" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="580" cy="400" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="580" y="390" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Decision Making</text>
                <text x="580" y="410" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Presenting roadmap</text>
                <text x="580" y="425" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">for approval</text>
                
                <!-- Execution -->
                <circle cx="400" cy="480" r="70" fill="#ea4335" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="400" cy="480" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="400" y="470" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Execution</text>
                <text x="400" y="490" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Migration in single</text>
                <text x="400" y="505" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">or multiple phases</text>
                
                <!-- Testing & Optimizing -->
                <circle cx="220" cy="400" r="70" fill="#ab47bc" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="220" cy="400" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="220" y="390" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Testing &</text>
                <text x="220" y="410" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Optimizing</text>
                <text x="220" y="430" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Performance,</text>
                <text x="220" y="445" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">security & usability</text>
                
                <!-- Post-Migration Support -->
                <circle cx="220" cy="200" r="70" fill="#0097a7" opacity="0.9"/>
                <circle cx="220" cy="200" r="60" fill="#ffffff"/>
                <text x="220" y="190" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Post-Migration</text>
                <text x="220" y="210" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Support</text>
                <text x="220" y="230" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">Monitoring &</text>
                <text x="220" y="245" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle" fill="#666">future-proofing</text>
                
                <!-- Improved Arrows that stop at circle boundaries -->
                <!-- Assessment to Planning -->
                <path d="M465 145 Q510 160 535 180" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Planning to Decision Making -->
                <path d="M580 270 Q580 320 580 330" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Decision Making to Execution -->
                <path d="M520 430 Q480 450 460 460" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Execution to Testing -->
                <path d="M340 450 Q300 435 280 425" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Testing to Post-Migration -->
                <path d="M220 330 Q220 280 220 270" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Post-Migration to Assessment -->
                <path d="M285 175 Q330 145 340 135" stroke="#333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrowhead)"/>
                
                <!-- Center Text -->
                <text x="400" y="285" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Seamless</text>
                <text x="400" y="310" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Migration</text>
                <text x="400" y="335" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="bold" fill="#333">Process</text>
                
                <!-- Arrowhead definition -->
                <defs>
                  <marker id="arrowhead" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="7" refX="9" refY="3.5" orient="auto">
                    <polygon points="0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7" fill="#333"/>
                  </marker>
                </defs>
              </svg>
        </div>
	</section>


    <section class="bg-gray-100 mx-2">
        <div class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto px-5 py-5 md:px-15 md:py-10 rounded-2xl text-center bg-white">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-5">Still have questions? Let's talk. Start Your Cloud Migration Journey.</p>
            <a href="#calendly-container" class="bg-primary-600 text-white py-2 px-5 rounded-lg transition">Book Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

